<br>
The point I was trying to make though is that when you have 2 procs on a weapon (augged), 3 things can happen every melee swing.<br>
<br>
1.) Weapon primary proc fires.  Secondary proc can not go off on this swing (there has yet to be /logged proof of both procs firing off of the same swing).<br>
<br>
2.) Primary proc does not fire, and secondary proc fires.<br>
<br>
3.) Neither proc fires.<br>
<br>
On a side note Artanis, I was looking at you Magelo, and to me it seems that your HP is going to be a bit lacking for what you would be tanking.  Two things I would do to change this would be to get Natural Durablility right away, and get some cheaper upgrades for some miscelaneous slots.<br>
<br>
Natural Durablility gave me a ton of HP, I don't remember how much exactly but it was over 600.<br>
<br>
As for upgrades, I'd say Runed Fang necklace for the neck (if you get a good price), 2 x Cultural bracers for the wrists, and any back item that has HP on it (look for more than 50 HP on the back).  You have a lot of items that have nothing but raw Stamina.  This is good, but remember that STA can be capped with buffs, while raw HP has no cap.  Feel free to look at my Magelo for some ideas too, but I worship the great Warlord, so that helps me a bit.  (From my profile, click on &quot;Modifiers&quot;, then take a look at all my slots by &quot;HP&quot;).  <br>
<br>
Also, get some stat food!  Halas 10 pound meat pie + Grobb liquidised meat would give you 30 HP, 11 STA, and other melee stats.<br>
